            "text": "nucleotides ( Figure 2 ), revealed that all positive samples by PCR belong to the species Human adenovirus B and are in the same cluster with adenovirus 7.",
            "cite_spans": [],
            "ref_spans": [
                {
                    "start": 14,
                    "end": 22,
                    "text": "Figure 2",
